summary:
- **Type:** Capital Raising Announcement (At-the-Market Placement)  
- **Capital Raised:** AUD $900,000 (inclusive of costs)  
- **Structure:** 110,000,000 shares issued at AUD 0.0082 per share (premium to last traded price of AUD 0.007)  
- **Use of Proceeds:** Funding construction of first production facility at Prairie Lithium Brine Project  
- **Issuance Method:** LR7.1 capacity
